        "mainbody": "'''Marigold''' was a [[dragon]].{{cite book/The Rite||12}}\n\nIn [[Flamerule]] of the {{yearlinkName|1373}}, Marigold slept in the [[Galena Mountains]] at a refuge for [[metallic dragon]]s waiting for the [[Rage of Dragons]] to end. After the duel between Lareth and [[Tamarand]], from which only the latter emerged alive, [[Nexus]] meant to wake Marigold up to tend to his wounds and [[Karasendrieth]]'s."
